      "lineId": "page_0128-l0013",
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "sourceStatus": "REDACTION_MARKER_CHECK",
      "sourceText": "Mr. [REDACTED] advised that as far as he knows, no one else in South Royalton saw these flying discs, and that he believes he saw them inasmuch as he has unusually good eyesight and that he can see bees, etc. further than anyone else. He stated that possibly these flying discs were out of the range of normal vision. Mr. [REDACTED] was asked to furnish any additional information that comes to his attention concerning these flying discs directly to the Air Forces since they now handle matters of this type.",
